             was indicted for <rs id="t17951028-22-off122" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17951028-22-off122" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17951028-22-off122" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17951028-22-cd123" type="crimeDate">28th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17951028-22-off122 t17951028-22-cd123"></join>, a pewter quart pot, value 1s. 6d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17951028-22-victim271" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Nurse
                  <interp inst="t17951028-22-victim271" type="surname" value="Nurse"></interp>
